reviewText: I don't understand why we are unable to purchase this show in region1 in fact the USA I've seen clips on you-tube, and HULU, why not sell it everywhere, great show!

This series should not have been cancelled. It's stories are great
as is the acting. And the setting is beautiful up here in British
Columbia. Don't forget to watch for Teryl Rothery from StarGate SG-1.
Or better known as Dr. Fraser.
